nodes.text: A group of insurgents emerged on the planet Denash in the Batonn sector during the Imperial Era. The Denash insurgents had ties with the Batonn insurgents and the Sammun insurgents. During the Batonn sector insurgency, the Denash insurgents evacuated most of their ships and materiel to Batonn. However, some stragglers were captured by Admiral Kinshara's One Twenty-Fifth task force. The other Denash insurgents were killed during the Batonn insurgency.
